    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Buana Finance Tbk provides investment, working capital, and multipurpose financing services in Indonesia. It operates through Finance Lease Receivables and Consumer Financing Receivables segments. The company offers financing services for various products, including heavy equipment, such as excavators, wheel loaders, tractors, and heavy trucks; generators and forklifts; printing and industrial machineries; consumer cars and commercial vehicles (trucks); vessels; Hajj/Umrah; education; tour traveling/vacation; and others, as well as sale and leaseback services. It also provides working capital financing, which includes factoring; multipurpose financing comprising finance lease, installment finance and funding facility; and investment financing that cover financing facilities for procurement of capital goods, as well as services to individuals, business entities, or legal entities for the modernization and expansion of businesses/investment. It serves customers through a network of 35 branches located in Jabodetabek, Java, Sumatera, Bali, Kalimantan, and Sulawesi. PT Buana Finance Tbk was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Buana Finance Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Sari Dasa Karsa.",
